        boolean hasQueryStats()
         Aggregated statistics from the execution of the query. Only present when
 the query is profiled. For example, a query could return the statistics as
 follows:
     {
       "rows_returned": "3",
       "elapsed_time": "1.22 secs",
       "cpu_time": "1.19 secs"
     }
